summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Forty-second Street from Brooklyn Avenue to Fifteenth Avenue Northeast, et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 19612, creating Local Improvement District No. 1898 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
